Package com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.barcode Description

Provides access to internal and external barcode readers.

Toughpad API supports a variety of barcode readers. Depending on the use case, different types of barcode readers can be used in a device independent manner, allowing ISV applications to focus on processing barcode data instead of managing hardware specific behaviors and protocols.
